01:01:22.543 --> 01:01:24.284
And I want to tell you,

01:01:24.405 --> 01:01:26.126
my impression then,

01:01:26.766 --> 01:01:28.367
and the same thing was true with Russia.

01:01:29.088 --> 01:01:29.929
The people are marvelous.

01:01:31.090 --> 01:01:32.871
We want to paint both as being boogeymen.

01:01:32.891 --> 01:01:33.791
They're just not.

01:01:34.393 --> 01:01:35.574
They're really lovely people.

01:01:35.653 --> 01:01:36.634
I did business for...

01:01:37.559 --> 01:01:39.045
