01:01:49.532 --> 01:01:50.614
industrial leader of the world.

01:01:51.114 --> 01:01:54.115
And my trip through the Soviet Union,

01:01:54.775 --> 01:01:56.516
escorted by Natasha Gerizkova,

01:01:56.577 --> 01:02:00.460
