01:02:23.670 --> 01:02:25.670
They had,

01:02:25.690 --> 01:02:29.934
you'd go into a store there and where

01:02:29.974 --> 01:02:30.896
we go into an American store,

01:02:30.916 --> 01:02:32.717
there may be fifty brands of toothpaste

01:02:32.878 --> 01:02:34.559
and every imaginable size,

01:02:34.599 --> 01:02:35.721
flavor and dispenser.

01:02:37.128 --> 01:02:40.070
There's one which is there sometimes which

01:02:40.090 --> 01:02:41.791
you have to line up when the shipment

01:02:41.811 --> 01:02:42.751
