01:02:42.771 --> 01:02:44.253
You know,

01:02:44.313 --> 01:02:46.594
everything deodorant there is one,

01:02:47.375 --> 01:02:48.175
not hundreds.

01:02:49.476 --> 01:02:53.280
It was horrible how much they were

01:02:53.300 --> 01:02:54.900
deprived just in their ordinary lives.

01:02:55.802 --> 01:02:57.063
They didn't get to choose where they live.

01:02:58.163 --> 01:02:59.443
They didn't get to choose what they wanted

01:02:59.463 --> 01:02:59.864
to read.

01:03:00.605 --> 01:03:01.826
They couldn't choose where they wanted to

01:03:01.865 --> 01:03:02.085
go.

01:03:02.706 --> 01:03:03.987
They could not choose where they wanted to

01:03:04.047 --> 01:03:04.288
work.

01:03:05.585 --> 01:03:06.706
and no freedoms in their lives.

01:03:07.507 --> 01:03:10.728
And what I noticed in both Red China

01:03:10.989 --> 01:03:16.572
and the Soviet Union is that because they

01:03:16.612 --> 01:03:17.833
were at war with religion,

01:03:18.333 --> 01:03:19.693
which later in my life I would also

01:03:19.713 --> 01:03:20.894
become at war with religion,

01:03:21.375 --> 01:03:26.617
but they replaced religion of pretend gods

01:03:27.177 --> 01:03:28.099
with religion of men.

01:03:29.538 --> 01:03:31.639
And so in Russia,

01:03:32.318 --> 01:03:36.280
Lenin and Marx and Stalin,

01:03:37.302 --> 01:03:38.342
they were all chiseled.

01:03:39.643 --> 01:03:44.824
The depictions of them were as the Greeks

01:03:44.864 --> 01:03:47.045
and the Romans presented their gods.

01:03:48.038 --> 01:03:49.659
And there was always, you know,

01:03:49.719 --> 01:03:50.740
Mao's Little Red Book.

01:03:51.260 --> 01:03:53.903
And there was the sayings of Lenin and

01:03:53.943 --> 01:03:54.403
Stalin.

01:03:54.824 --> 01:03:56.947
And people had to memorize these.

01:03:57.246 --> 01:03:59.208
They sung their songs in the morning,

01:03:59.289 --> 01:04:02.512
glorifying these hideous, murderous,

01:04:02.753 --> 01:04:05.576
deceitful, counterproductive men.

01:04:06.811 --> 01:04:09.014
And so there were statues and billboards

01:04:09.634 --> 01:04:10.454
and everything,

01:04:10.855 --> 01:04:14.518
everything was just placard by these four

01:04:14.557 --> 01:04:15.798
men, Mao in China.

01:04:16.239 --> 01:04:17.420
And but also in China,

01:04:17.481 --> 01:04:20.702
you also had Lenin and Marx.

01:04:21.143 --> 01:04:22.485
And in Russia, it was Marx,

01:04:22.605 --> 01:04:23.425
Lenin and Stalin.

01:04:23.965 --> 01:04:26.288
And you could not have three worse men.

01:04:27.489 --> 01:04:28.588
They turned men into gods,

01:04:28.670 --> 01:04:31.251
and so communism became the religion of

01:04:31.291 --> 01:04:31.492
man.

01:04:33.686 --> 01:04:36.367
and the oppression and the poverty.

01:04:36.827 --> 01:04:39.467
We went to places where they didn't even

01:04:39.507 --> 01:04:40.286
have indoor plumbing.

01:04:43.487 --> 01:04:44.708
People were still coming to wells,

01:04:44.748 --> 01:04:47.628
they were still in donkeys.

01:04:47.648 --> 01:04:49.509
There was a facade of a country that

01:04:49.528 --> 01:04:52.989
could send up a rocket with Gregorian and

01:04:53.108 --> 01:04:55.150
that could make an atomic bomb.

01:04:55.630 --> 01:04:57.329
But underneath it all,

01:04:57.670 --> 01:04:59.831
it was just total poverty.

